channel.title: Jbirdscape
channel.description:
[url=http://jbirdscape.org/forums/play.php][img]http://i49.tinypic.com/fa38f7.png[/img][/url]
[url=http://jbirdscape.org/forums/]Forums[/url] [url=http://jbirdscape.org/forums/play.php]Play Now[/url]
[size=14pt]Introduction[/size] [i] Jbirdscape is one of the oldest private servers out there, however these newer players might not know too much of whom we are. Jbirdscape also has great uptime which is close to near 100% which can never be 100% due to downtime causes. Never offline too long though. We are also a great community and hope to see any new players come join. This server has been coming and going since 2006. However this is the return that changed everything.
This server is a 317 deob, which has great features and way more updates too come. Below you will find a spoiler full of pictures, the pictures might not be the best but its something. Theres so many features that i didnt exactly know what to take pictures of. So please if you would come visit us at the links posted above.
Suggestions are a huge part of this server, however this is not just a server created by the owner but also the players. The players have a huge say so in what in created or added to the server. Each and every suggestion will be read and actually suggested. If the idea grabs my attention like it should then there will be a poll posted for a week and however the community responds to that suggestion depends on whether or not it will be added.
This community will be as helpful as possible to each and every player which has ongoing projects that all players can be involved in on. The projects arent just RSPS related. Its tons of fun! Just a quick click away from being part of this great community. Thank you for taking time out and reading this topic. Hope to see you online! [/i]
[size=14pt]Features[/size] - These are just a few features i could think up while creating this topic. [i] - Custom Minigames - Grand Exchange - Great PKing - Tons of dungeons - All 317 skills - Fixed/Resized/Fullscreen - Clipped Players - Clipped NPCs - Skill Icon Teleports [/i]
[img]http://i50.tinypic.com/2nl4ehg.png[/img] [img]http://i50.tinypic.com/23tl7xt.png[/img] [img]http://i50.tinypic.com/2j4ocxg.png[/img] [img]http://i47.tinypic.com/2qxtg8h.png[/img] [img]http://i50.tinypic.com/35b83g4.png[/img] [img]http://i48.tinypic.com/10s4ry8.png[/img] [img]http://i46.tinypic.com/10igls5.png[/img] [img]http://i47.tinypic.com/2ur4ax3.png[/img] [img]http://i45.tinypic.com/2iaubua.png[/img] [img]http://i45.tinypic.com/2gslnut.png[/img] [img]http://i49.tinypic.com/30af987.png[/img]
Hopefully i didnt miss anything. If you wish to see this topic changed in any way please give some feedback. Also if you do not like what you see on this topic please do not leave a rude post. Please give only positive feedback.
Thank you very much!
- Jbird

item.dc:creator: @Dokan42 Dokan42
item.description:
@Dokan42 wrote:

[quote=“deathschaos9, post:32, topic:479702”]I have deeply loved Jbirdscape since I started playing back in Silabsoft days. I also loved your first delta version of Jbirdscape and for a brief moment I was number one on your hiscores…

Jbirdstats.jpg463×613

That is one of the oldest pictures I have, and it is from your old website…

Justin (Jbird), you have my utmost respect and your server peaked my interest in private servers and without it I would probably be in law school rather than majoring in computer programming. You helped me discover my inner nerd and though I highly doubt you remember me I was once a co-owner on your Silab server. I never got into playing private servers except this one, where Ranger Owns was my name.

At any rate, I have high expectations for this server and wish you the best of luck.[/quote]
I lost faith in Jbird, I played his server and contributed, but at the same time, I was developing my own server. Of course, I take a break from Jbirdscape, and Jbird decides to come on my server, advertising his own… He then bans me from his site…
Let alone, he is constantly asking for donations…
